flowchart TD
    raw[Raw vertex features] --> walk[Walk-conv layer<br/>HG-conv over w_2, w_3, ...]
    walk -->|Clifford-FIR transfer<br/>grade 1 → 2| poly[Polygon-conv layer<br/>HG-conv over c_4, c_5, c_6, ...]
    poly -->|Clifford-FIR transfer<br/>grade 2 → 3| tri[Triangle-conv layer<br/>HG-conv over c_3<br/>+ Cartwright-Harary gate]
    tri --> abs[Abstraction-conv<br/>derivative-nodelet contraction<br/>balanced clique → super-vertex]
    abs --> head[Task head]
    abs -.->|recurse on contracted graph| walk

    subgraph gomb["Gömb (cognitive-stack, kept canonical)"]
        outer[OuterFIRShell<br/>geometric]
        middle[MiddleHSiKAN<br/>learnable nonlinearity]
        inner[InnerCPMLCore<br/>routing]
        head1[head]
        outer --> middle --> inner --> head1
    end

    classDef walkClass fill:#fed7aa,stroke:#c2410c,color:#000
    classDef polyClass fill:#bfdbfe,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#000
    classDef triClass fill:#bbf7d0,stroke:#15803d,color:#000
    classDef absClass fill:#e9d5ff,stroke:#7e22ce,color:#000
    classDef headClass fill:#e5e7eb,stroke:#000,color:#000
    classDef rawClass fill:#f3f4f6,stroke:#6b7280,color:#000
    class walk walkClass
    class poly polyClass
    class tri triClass
    class abs absClass
    class head,head1 headClass
    class raw rawClass

